{"lemma":"سُفْلُ","slug":"سُفْلُ","root":"س.ف.ل","root_slug":"س-ف-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ف-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19996","n20000","n20001","n20002"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8F%D9%81%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19996","headword_ar":"سَفَلَ","root":"sfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, MA, Mgh, O, * Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safula","text_ar":"سَفُلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safila","text_ar":"سَفِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) inf. n. (of the first, Mgh, Msb, TA, and of the last, TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sufuwlN","text_ar":"سُفُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, MA, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safaAlN","text_ar":"سَفَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, MA, K, TA, in the CK [erroneously]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sifAl","text_ar":"سِفال"},{"kind":"text","text":",) and of the second"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safaAlapN","text_ar":"سَفَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tsf~l","text_ar":"تسفّل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, low;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, * Mgh, O, K; *) the first"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaA","text_ar":"عَلَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, O;) and the third, of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaliYa","text_ar":"عَلِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and (assumed tropical:)  both are said of a man; (O;)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sufuwlN","text_ar":"سُفُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safaAlN","text_ar":"سَفَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being the contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euluw~N","text_ar":"عُلُوٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalA='N","text_ar":"عَلا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became lower than another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) [and] the first signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it descended, subsided,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sank downwards."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.) Hence the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"binotu binoti binotK","text_ar":"بِنْتُ بِنْتِ بِنْتٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA_ino safalato","text_ar":"وَاـِنْ سَفَلَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A daughter of a daughter of a daughter, and if she be lower in descent"},{"kind":"text","text":"]:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safulato","text_ar":"سَفُلَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. with damm to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"f","text_ar":"ف"},{"kind":"text","text":", in this case, is a mistake. (Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safalato manozilatuhu Einoda AlA^amiyri","text_ar":"سَفَلَتْ مَنْزِلَتُهُ عِنْدَ الاَمِيرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His station with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the estimation of, the commander, governor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prince, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, low,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amoruhumo fiYsafaAlK","text_ar":"اَمْرُهُمْ فِىسَفَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Their case is in a low state"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safala fiYAl$~Yo'i","text_ar":"سَفَلَ فِىالشّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, * TA, [in the former of which the context implies that it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safula","text_ar":"سَفُلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but it is]) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSara","text_ar":"نَصَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sufuwlN","text_ar":"سُفُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It subsided in the thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it descended from the upper,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uppermost, part of the thing, to the lower,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest, part thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safula","text_ar":"سَفُلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safaAlapN","text_ar":"سَفَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, S, MA, Mgh, O, K *) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safaAliyapN","text_ar":"سَفَالِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sufolN","text_ar":"سُفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, O,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, low, base, vile, ignoble, mean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sordid;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, S, MA, Mgh, O, K; *) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safala","text_ar":"سَفَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h, (Fr, O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safila","text_ar":"سَفِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (MA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safala","text_ar":"سَفَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatala","text_ar":"قَتَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safula","text_ar":"سَفُلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"karuma","text_ar":"كَرُمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY xuluqihi","text_ar":"فِى خُلُقِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamalihi","text_ar":"عَمَلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nasabihi","text_ar":"نَسَبِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) [aor. in either case"},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safolN","text_ar":"سَفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sufolN","text_ar":"سُفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sifaAlN","text_ar":"سِفَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, * K, [in the former without any indication of the syll. signs,]) the last like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbN","text_ar":"كِتَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) [and app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safila","text_ar":"سَفِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also accord. to the MA, as shown above;] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tsf~l","text_ar":"تسفّل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astfl","text_ar":"استفل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was low, base, vile, ignoble,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mean, in his lot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or, as seems to be indicated in the Msb,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inferior to others,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of his disposition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his deed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his lineage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tsf~l","text_ar":"تسفّل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAda","text_ar":"جَادَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K","M","MA","Mgh","Msb","S","TA","Fr"]},{"entry_id":"n20000","headword_ar":"سُفْلٌ","root":"sfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sifolN","text_ar":"سِفْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, O, Msb, K) [but it is strangely added in the Msb that IKt disallowed the pronunciation with damm] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sifolapN","text_ar":"سِفْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sufaAlahN","text_ar":"سُفَالَهٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower, part"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of a thing];"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EulowN","text_ar":"عُلْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, O, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EilowN","text_ar":"عِلْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, O, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EilowapN","text_ar":"عِلْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EulaAwapN","text_ar":"عُلَاوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K;) [and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAflapN","text_ar":"سَافلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAlyapN","text_ar":"عَاليَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kul~ $aYo'K","text_ar":"كُلّ شَىْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sufaAlahu","text_ar":"سُفَالَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies, (K,) or is said to signify, (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the lowest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower, part of anything;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asofaluhu","text_ar":"اَسْفَلُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EulaAwatuhu","text_ar":"عُلَاوَتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[The contr., i. e.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolaAhu","text_ar":"اَعْلَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Mgh","O","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n20001","headword_ar":"سِفْلٌ","root":"sfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n20002","headword_ar":"سَفِلٌ","root":"sfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safila","text_ar":"سَفِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safiylN","text_ar":"سَفِيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safula","text_ar":"سَفُلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)  A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"low, base, vile, ignoble, mean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sordid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"man: (MA:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safylN","text_ar":"سَفيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"low"},{"kind":"text","text":"(↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAfilN","text_ar":"سَافِلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":") [in"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deficient in lot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fortune:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safilapN","text_ar":"سَفِلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, MA, Mgh, Msb, K,) said by some to be from this word as signifying the “ legs ” (Mgh, Msb) of a camel (Mgh) or of a beast, or quadruped, (Msb,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sifolapN","text_ar":"سِفْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, MA, Mgh Msb, K,) a contraction of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safilapN","text_ar":"سَفِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, or it may be pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safiylN","text_ar":"سَفِيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiloyapN","text_ar":"عِلْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaliY~N","text_ar":"عَلِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"low, base, vile, ignoble, mean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sordid, persons;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * MA, Mgh, Msb;) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower, basest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"baser, vilest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"viler,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., of mankind, or of people; the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"refuse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rabble,"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof: (S, * M, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sifilapN","text_ar":"سِفِلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with two kesrehs, is a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safilapN","text_ar":"سَفِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sifolapN","text_ar":"سِفْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", mentioned by Sgh and IB on the authority of Yoo and IKh, and is said to mean the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest, basest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the low, base,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: the pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sifolapN","text_ar":"سِفْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sifalN","text_ar":"سِفَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) one should not say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa safilapN","text_ar":"هُوَ سَفِلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"because this is [used only as] a pl.: (S:) the vulgar say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino qawomK sifalK","text_ar":"مِنْ قَوْمٍ سِفَلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sifolapN","text_ar":"سِفْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Mgh; *) but this has been disallowed: (Mgh:) a man is related to have said to his wife, (Mgh, TA,) who had called him"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sifolapN","text_ar":"سِفْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ino kunotu sifolapF faA^anoti TaAliqN","text_ar":"اـِنْ كُنْتُ سِفْلَةً فَاَنْتِ طَالِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, TA,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If I be low, base,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in my intellect and my religion"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thou art divorced"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Mgh;) whence it seems that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sifolapN","text_ar":"سِفْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be applied to a single person; but this requires consideration. (TA.) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ayomaAnu Als~afilapi","text_ar":"اَيْمَانُ السَّفِلَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The oaths"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the ignorant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or accord. to Aboo- Haneefeh,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the heretics,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"schismatics:"},{"kind":"text","text":"such [oaths] are said to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wawajohi A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"وَوَجْهِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA^maAnapi A@ll~`h","text_ar":"وَامَانَةِ ا@للّٰه"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh.)"}],"source_refs":["MA","TA","S","M","Mgh","Msb","K"]}]}}